content:
The calendar says,
"Thursday is suitable for staying at home."{短暂停}
Alright, let's head out and have some fun!

Yay, it's Friday and tomorrow's Saturday.
I'm so happy, {短暂停}
Just kidding.

I heard that in some bubbles,
Sunday is a day of rest.{短暂停}
Why can't the other days be rest days too?
